    "examples": [
      {
        "example": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "Example:",
            "spans": []
          },
          {
            "type": "preformatted",
            "text": "Of course we should buy IBM's computer whenever we need new computers. We have been buying IBM as far back as anyone can remember.",
            "spans": []
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "text": "The \"of course\" is the problem. The traditional wisdom of IBM being the right buy is some reason to buy IBM next time, but it's not a good enough reason in a climate of changing products, so the \"of course\" indicates that the fallacy of Traditional Wisdom has occurred.",
